- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with autonomous agents and collision avoidance in urban environments.

- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper mentions object recognition errors and missed frames in the trajectory data. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with autonomous agents and their ability to predict collisions. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper deals with the safety of autonomous agents in urban environments.
